      "instruction": "<p>Set aside 1 <strong>whole lettuce leaf</strong> per person, then tear the <strong>remaining lettuce leaves</strong> roughly</p><p>Grate your<strong> cheddar flavour block[s]</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>grated cheeze</strong> with your <strong>cornflour</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a pot and mix until the cheeze is fully coated</p><p>Add your <strong>mustard ketchup</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> to the pot and set aside for later – this is your <strong>cheeze sauce base</strong></p>",
