      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>meat-free patty[ies]</strong> and your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Mix until combined, then divide and shape them into 2 meatballs per person (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Cover the<strong> meatballs</strong> with a sheet of<strong> baking paper</strong> and roll the meatballs out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until evenly flattened – these are your <strong>patties</strong></p>",
